{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "elector360-api-v1",
    "name": "Elector360 API",
    "description": "Colección de endpoints para el sistema de gestión electoral Elector360.\n\n## Autenticación\nLa mayoría de endpoints requieren autenticación JWT. Usa el endpoint de Login para obtener el token y configúralo en la variable `{{token}}`.\n\n## Variables\n- `{{base_url}}`: URL base de la API\n- `{{token}}`: Token JWT de autenticación",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Endpoints de autenticación",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('Token guardado automáticamente');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@elector360.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Iniciar sesión y obtener token JWT.\n\n**Credenciales de prueba:**\n- Admin: admin@elector360.com / password123\n- Líder: lider1@elector360.com / lider123456"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Renovar token JWT usando refresh token."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Me (Perfil actual)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
